user.bio: Beer, whiskey and coffee are my loves! I use the uni scoring system for my ratings, and love both strong and light beers

items.badge_description: Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 175 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 36!

It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That's 260 check-ins with a photo.  Try 5 more for Level 53!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 135 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 28! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

items.checkin_comment: Can claims 6.4 abv. Malted flavours, deep red colour, great drinking.

items.checkin_comment: Rich, bit hoppy, bit resinous. Good flavour.
